{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2344 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2344 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[618,638],"content":"Compiler Error C2344","linkify":"Compiler Error C2344","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2344","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"align(#) : alignment must be power of two","pos":[639,680]},{"pos":[687,785],"content":"When using the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>align<ept id=\"p1\">](../../cpp/align-cpp.md)</ept> keyword, the value you pass must be a power of two.","source":"When using the [align](../../cpp/align-cpp.md) keyword, the value you pass must be a power of two."},{"content":"For example, the following code generates C2344 because 3 is not a power of two:","pos":[792,872]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2344 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2344\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2344\"\nms.assetid: a84c7b37-c84e-4345-8691-c23abb2dc193\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2344\nalign(#) : alignment must be power of two  \n  \n When using the [align](../../cpp/align-cpp.md) keyword, the value you pass must be a power of two.  \n  \n For example, the following code generates C2344 because 3 is not a power of two:  \n  \n```  \n// C2344.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \n__declspec(align(3)) int a;   // C2344  \n__declspec(align(4)) int b;   // OK  \n```"}